Nebulous Rules
 
 1. Do not share or trade accounts with anyone. This will result in both players being permanently banned.
 2. Do not ask for accounts from anyone. This will result in you being permanently banned.
 3. Do not pretend to be a Moderator or Youtuber. This will result in you being permanently banned.
 4. Do not cheat to reach the top ranking of the game in clan wars or arena (FreePoints). This will reset your stats and result in a permanent ban.
 5. Never ask for the leader rank in a Clan.
 6. Do not insult anyone.
 7. Do not create Custom Games Chats with inappropriate names.
 8. Obey the Moderators.
 9. Do not take advantage of bugs in the game.
 10. Do not ban many clan Members without the leader's authorization.
 11. In team games do not team up with someone on an opposing team.
 12. Never lie to a Moderator.
 13. Do not exchange Nebulous Clans for money or plasma.
 14. Do not spam in chat or mail.
 
 If you do not comply with any of these rules your account could be banned.
 (The time of punishment can be from few hours to permanent ban, depending of the situation and severity of the problem).
 
 If you notice a player breaking the rules of the game please report it to a Moderator.

"CUSTOM SKINS
When you buy a custom skin the quality of the image will decrease, but this is not of great importance and is normal (almost no difference when you play).
In Review (Yellow): Means that the skin is being reviewed, you must wait for it to be approved.
Approved (Green): The skin can be seen by other players.
Reimbursed (Orange): You received a refund of the skin, because it does not meet the established standards, you must select some other image that is not the same.
Rejected (Red): It means that your skin can not be seen by other players because it has inappropriate content, you will not be returned the plasma.
WHY WAS MY CUSTOM SKIN REIMBURSED OR REJECTED?
If your custom skin is reimbursed, do not buy it again because it will be rejected and you will lose your plasma.
This is a list of things that is * PROHIBITED * to use in the custom skins. If you buy a skin with this it will be reimbursed or rejected: - Content and / or some Sexual reference - Unmodified Nebulous Skins / Art - Content Gore / Suicide - Nudes (no shirt) - Very dark skins - Transparent skins - Drugs (Alcohol / Cigars / Marijuana) - Name of pages for adults (pornography) - People with little clothes (necklines on the body) - Racism / Nazism / Violence - People using a weapon - Obscene signals with hands"

1. A photograph of a person as a community skin. It can be a non-community skin. 2. A photograph of someone shirtless. 3. Someone in a suggestive pose or scene. 4. Depictions of alcohol or drugs (including weed). 5. Artwork that already exists in nebulous such as level skins. It must be modified in some meaningful way.
